ParcellationEntityVersion

https://openminds.ebrains.eu/sands/ParcellationEntityVersion

part of SANDS in version v3 - view as JSON Schema

Required properties are highlighted in bold
propertyvalue
name*descriptiontypeinstruction
name Word or phrase that constitutes the distinctive designation of a being or thing. string Enter the name of this parcellation entity version.
versionIdentifier Term or code used to identify the version of something. string Enter the version identifier of this parcellation entity version.
abbreviation string Enter the official abbreviation of this parcellation entity version.
additionalRemarks Mention of what deserves additional attention or notice. string Enter any additional remarks concerning this parcellation entity version.
alternateName array (1 - n) of type:
string		 Enter any alternate names, including any alternative abbreviations, for this parcellation entity version.
correctedName string Enter the refined or corrected name of this parcellation entity version.
hasAnnotation embedded object array (1 - n) of type:
AtlasAnnotation 		Add all atlas annotations which define this parcellation entity version.
hasParent Reference to a parent object or legal person. linked object array (1 - n) of type:
ParcellationEntity OR
ParcellationEntityVersion 		Add all anatomical parent structures (or version of the structures) for this parcellation entity as defined within corresponding brain atlas version.
lookupLabel string Enter a lookup label for this parcellation entity version that may help you to find this instance more easily.
ontologyIdentifier Term or code used to identify something or someone registered within a particular ontology. array (1 - n) of type:
string (format: iri)		 Enter the internationalized resource identifiers (IRIs) to the related ontological terms matching this parcellation entity version.
relationAssessment embedded object array (1 - n) of type:
QualitativeRelationAssessment OR
QuantitativeRelationAssessment 		Add all relations (qualitative or quantitative) of this parcellation entity version to other anatomical entities.
versionInnovation Documentation on what changed in comparison to a previously published form of something. string Enter a short description (or summary) of the novelties/peculiarities of this parcellation entity version in comparison to its preceding versions. If this parcellation entity version is the first version, leave blank.
*This is the simplified property name - within a metadata instance of this schema (JSON-LD) the properties are extended to map to the openMINDS vocabulary namespace ("https://openminds.ebrains.eu/vocab/PROPERTY_NAME").
